    - add support for %(*ver)s and %(*shortver)s templates (#1595, #1604)
        - incl. %(javaver)s, %(javashortver)s, %(perlver)s, %(perlshortver)s, %(pyver)s, %(pyshortver)s, %(rver)s, %(rshortver)s
